		<description><![CDATA[This is nitpicky, and I certainly don&#8217;t mean to take lightly the seriousness of the matter. But I do want to clarify that the News of the World wasn&#8217;t technically &#8220;hacking&#8221; voicemail in its scandal. It was engaged in social engineering. For those of you who missed the headlines (and for the benefit of posterity): [...]


