		<title>Good Contracts Make Good Business. Or, ‘F*ck You, Pay Me’</title>
		<link>http://www.dougv.com/2011/04/16/good-contracts-make-good-business-or-fck-you-pay-me/</link>
		<comments>http://www.dougv.com/2011/04/16/good-contracts-make-good-business-or-fck-you-pay-me/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 16 Apr 2011 16:15:49 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Doug Vanderweide</dc:creator>
